data.name: selectImagesInstructionsLabel.Text
data.value:
Instructions:
(1) Use only PNG images. (2) Rename the images you want to use using numbers only. ie: 1.PNG, 2.PNG, 3.PNG, etc... (3) Place your images into a new folder. (4) Optional But Recommended: Place your new folder into the Custom Desktop Logo directory under the "System" -> "Images" folder. This enables you to use Custom Desktop Logo on other computers while keeping all your images intact. (5) Click the "Change Image Folder" button to browse to the directory of your images.
